        "when": "Emails and launch copy where ownership matters; acceptable in blog posts when the agent is genuinely unknown or unimportant",
        "example_before": "The decision was made to delay the rollout.",
        "example_after": "We decided to delay the rollout."
      },
      {
        "rule": "Cut 'it's important to,' 'it's worth noting,' 'needless to say,' 'it should be mentioned' \u2014 assert directly",
